OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1777723866
OL,3,CMan jailed for attempted rape and
OL,4,Cstrangulation of woman in Bradford
OL,6,FA man has been given an extended 18-
OL,7,Fand-a-half-year sentence for
OL,8,Fattempting to rape a woman at a
OL,9,FBradford park.
OL,11,FKhairul Amin, 36, of Moor View Drive
OL,12,Fwas convicted of attempt rape,
OL,13,Fintentional strangulation and assault
OL,14,Foccasioning actual bodily harm.
OL,16,FThe victim, a woman in her 30s, rang
OL,17,Fpolice at around 9pm on 28 August to
OL,18,Freport that she had been attacked,
OL,19,Fsexually assaulted and strangled by an
OL,20,Funknown man in Peel Park.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
