FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1777723866
OL,3,CMan jailed for attempted rape and
OL,4,Cstrangulation of woman in Bradford
OL,6,FThe victim suffered serious head
OL,7,Finjuries and was treated in hospital.
OL,9,FIn a victim impact statement read to
OL,10,Fthe court, she said the attack ruined
OL,11,Fher life:
OL,13,F"It has ruined my day-to-day life. I
OL,14,Fam still having flashbacks regularly.
OL,15,FI hope the sentence he receives
OL,16,Freflects the pain, trauma and loss of
OL,17,Fconfidence that I have endured since
OL,18,Fthe assault.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,362,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F361A1777723866
OL,3,CMan jailed for attempted rape and
OL,4,Cstrangulation of woman in Bradford
OL,6,FShe added, "I hope that he never gets
OL,7,Fthe chance to rob any other person of
OL,8,Ftheir life, as he to mine."
OL,10,FAmin was given an extended sentence of
OL,11,F18 and a half years.
OL,13,FHe must serve 14 and a half years in
OL,14,Fjail before being considered for
OL,15,Fparole and the rest will be on licence.
OL,17,FDC Sue Sutcliffe of Bradford District
OL,18,FSafeguarding Unit said he was
OL,19,Farrested, charged and brought before
OL,20,Fthe courts within a day.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/4
