OL,3,CMan jailed for attempted rape and
OL,4,Cstrangulation of woman in Bradford
OL,6,FShe said, "He was described in court
OL,7,Fas a dangerous individual. I would
OL,8,Furge anyone who has been the victim of
OL,9,Fa sexual offence, to please report it
OL,10,Fto us so we can take action."
